    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i've been noticing lately how much slower everyone seems to process things compared to me. even in simple discussions, i can see the logic paths 10 steps ahead while everyone else is just struggling to catch up. it feels like my brain just operates on a completely different frequency or biological level. it's actually getting pretty frustrating because i feel like all these current social equity initiatives are basically designed to drag people like me down to the lowest common denominator just so everyone feels \"equal.\" feels like a massive waste of potential.",
